**🔎 Key Findings **
  -> Customers in first 6 months show highest churn.
  -> Low usage customers churn 3x more.
  -> Customers with high support calls show higher churn.
  -> Premium plans have higher churn.

**💡 Recommendations **
  -> Improve onboarding journey.
  -> Launch engagement campaigns for low-usage users.
  -> Improve customer support resolution.
  -> Promote annual subscription discounts.
